<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="4Apr1929"><font color="red">4 April 1929</font> <i>SIBS</i> (to Caresse and Harry Crosbie): I hereby acknowledge the receipt from you of &hellip; $1,000 &hellip; being the one-half payment &hellip; for the publication of the three fragments &hellip; &lsquo;The Ondt &amp; Gracehoper&rsquo;, &lsquo;Mookes and Gripes&rsquo;, &lsquo;The Triangle&rsquo;, to be edited by the Black Sun Press &hellip; The corrected proofs of these fragments will be [the Crosbies&apos;] property. </div>
